"In 1991, the United States and the then-Soviet Union, as a political commitment, voluntarily_agreed_to_cease_deploying_@REL any nuclear sea-launched_cruise_missiles_@WEA on surface_ships_@WEA or multipurpose_submarines_@WEA.
