"There's no comparison," said Daniel_Sneider_@P1, the associate_director_@REL for research at the Walter_H._Shorenstein_Asia-Pacific_Research_Center_@ORG at_@REL Stanford_University_@ORG in California, commenting on the Obama_administration_@ORG's approach versus that of its predecessor.
