There are six aircraft_@WEA carrier strike groups and the U.S._Pacific_Fleet_@ORG, which conducts_@REL regular joint_military_exercises_@PROG with Asian allies.When the Obama_administration_@ORG got serious about the pivot in 2010, Boston_College's_Ross_@P1 said, "you couldn't have asked for a more robust strategic presence than we had at the time.
