Among the report's author_@P2s are Gary Dirks, director_@REL of ASU's Global Institute of Sustainability, and consortium_co-director_@REL Daniel Sarewitz.Through a series of detailed maps, High-Energy_Innovation_@DOC charts_@REL energy_innovation_in_shale_gas_@TECH, carbon_capture_and_storage_@TECH, nuclear, and solar_@TECH currently underway worldwide.
