@REL  Manufacturing Technology (ManTech) program accepted_@REL the Department of Defense's_@REL Joint Defense Manufacturing Technology Achievement Award at the Defense Manufacturing Conference in San Antonio.The Department of Defense's_@REL Joint_Strike_Fighter_program_@PROG is_developing_@REL the next generation of affordable, lethal strike aircraft_@WEA in variants for the Navy_@ORG, Air Force and Marine_Corps_@ORG.
